# config/scopri_theme_map.conf.example
# SANITIZED TEMPLATE — no real PI names (see config/SITE_OVERRIDE.md).
# Real copy: config/site/scopri_theme_map.conf (gitignored).
# Deployed to: ${ARCHIVE_CONF_DIR}/scopri_theme_map.conf (=${BIOME_CONF}/conf/).
#
# Theme→supervisor inference map for scopri_progetti.sh.
# Format per row (separator ';' — grep patterns already use '|' for alternation):
#   <grep_-iE_pattern>;<supervisor_username>;<theme>
#   - pattern is matched against the user's cleaned AD group names (grep -iE)
#   - first matching row wins
#   - blank rows and rows starting with '#' are ignored
#   - no file (or no match) → supervisor resolves to _UNKNOWN_ (manual PI check)
#
# Examples (replace usernames/themes with your real values in config/site/):
\bflor\b|\blifewatch\b|\bBIOMAC\b|\bSGBGA\b;pi.username.one;floristica-macroecologia
\bremote\b|\bspatial\b|\bteleril\b;pi.username.two;telerilevamento
\blichen\b|\blicen\b;pi.username.three;lichenologia
\balghe\b|\balgae\b|\bciano\b;pi.username.four;alghe-cianobatteri
\bconserv\b;pi.username.five;conservazione
\bpaesagg\b|\blandscape\b;pi.username.six;paesaggio
\bPRIN2022\b;pi.username.seven;PRIN2022
